12) Explain what is the use of \ldblquote Move Issue\rdblquote  wizard in JIRA?\par
\par
The move issue wizard enables you to specify another project in your JIRA instance. Move wizard permit you to change certain attributes of an issue like\par
\par
Issue Type: If your issue is a custom issue type and does not occur in your target project, you must choose a new issue type for your issue\par
Issue Status: If you have assigned your issue as a custom issue status and it does not exist in your project, you must select a new issue status for your issue\par
Custom Fields: If you have determined required custom fields for your issue, which do not occur in the target project, you must set values for them.\par
13) How security setting is helpful in JIRA?\par
\par
